Classes for combination plots.

Interface Summary
AxisRange Interface used by CombinedPlot to represent the min/max range of an axis.
CombinableAxis Interface implemented by all CombinedXXXXXAxis classes.
 

Class Summary
AbstractAxisRange Abstract implementation of AxisRange interface.
CombinedChart A CombinedChart can be added to a CombinedPlot.
CombinedHorizontalDateAxis A combined horizontal date axis used internally by CombinedPlot.
CombinedHorizontalNumberAxis A combined horizontal number axis used internally by CombinedPlot.
CombinedHorizontalSymbolicAxis A combined horizontal Symbolic axis combines one or more HorizontalSymbolicAxes and aligns them for use in a CombinedPlot.
CombinedPlot This plot implements a combined plot that can contain one or more CombinedChart objects.
CombinedVerticalNumberAxis A combined vertical number axis combines one or more VerticalNumberAxes and aligns them for use in a CombinedPlot.
CombinedVerticalSymbolicAxis A combined vertical Symbolic axis combines one or more VerticalSymbolicAxes and aligns them for use in a CombinedPlot.
